title: Intel's Revival Plan Runs Into Trouble. 'We Had Some Serious Issues.'

title: AI Threat Placed on Par With Pandemics, Nuclear War
description: Tech executives and artificial-intelligence scientists are sounding the alarm about AI, saying that the technology poses an extinction risk as great as pandemics and nuclear war.
